        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://salif.github.io/zola-themes-collection/demo/halcyon/posts/test/"/>
        <id>https://salif.github.io/zola-themes-collection/demo/halcyon/posts/test/</id>
        
        <content type="html" xml:base="https://salif.github.io/zola-themes-collection/demo/halcyon/posts/test/">&lt;p&gt;This is just a quick and dirty test&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;math&quot;&gt;Math&lt;a class=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; href=&quot;#math&quot;&gt;#&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maths is rendered by KaTex&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Inline math: $f(a,b,c) = (a^2+b^2+c^2)^3$&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Block math:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;
$$f(a,b,c) = (a^2+b^2+c^2)^3$$&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you wanted to use maths you need to ensure it&#x27;s enabled when writing the post:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;yaml&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#151515;color:#e8e8d3;&quot; class=&quot;language-yaml &quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-yaml&quot; data-lang=&quot;yaml&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;[&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#99ad6a;&quot;&gt;extra&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;]
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#99ad6a;&quot;&gt;maths = true
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will call the KaTex auto-render extension CDN and math contained in the following tags will be rendered accordingly:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre style=&quot;background-color:#151515;color:#e8e8d3;&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;$math$ for inline math
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$$math$$ for display math
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;images&quot;&gt;Images&lt;a class=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; href=&quot;#images&quot;&gt;#&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Images should be pretty self explainitory, for personal preference I&#x27;ve set images to center themselves subject to size on the page&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;salif.github.io&#x2F;zola-themes-collection&#x2F;demo&#x2F;halcyon&#x2F;posts&#x2F;test&#x2F;images&#x2F;1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;youtube-shortcode&quot;&gt;Youtube shortcode&lt;a class=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; href=&quot;#youtube-shortcode&quot;&gt;#&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&#x27;ve also added a youtube shorcode. It&#x27;s set up with a few handy defaults and takes a video ID.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;iframe
	class=&quot;video&quot;
	src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.youtube-nocookie.com&#x2F;embed&#x2F;6BBgKWJRx1o&quot;
	title=&quot;YouTube video&quot;
	frameborder=&quot;0&quot;
	allow=&quot;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share&quot;
	allowfullscreen&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Usage:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;markdown&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#151515;color:#e8e8d3;&quot; class=&quot;language-markdown &quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-markdown&quot; data-lang=&quot;markdown&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{ youtube(id=&amp;quot;6BBgKWJRx1o&amp;quot;) } # This would be double curly brackets
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;github-repos&quot;&gt;Github Repos&lt;a class=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; href=&quot;#github-repos&quot;&gt;#&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lastly the only other shortcode I&#x27;ve implimented is github repos:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rust:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;doublespace&quot; data-owner=&quot;rust-lang&quot; data-repo=&quot;rust&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;repo-header&quot;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;rust-lang&#x2F;rust&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;
      rust-lang&#x2F;rust
    &lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;repo-stats small secondary&quot;&gt;
      &lt;span class=&quot;stars&quot;&gt;
        &lt;svg width=&quot;16&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 576 512&quot; fill=&quot;currentColor&quot;&gt;
          &lt;path d=&quot;M287.9 0c9.2 0 17.6 5.2 21.6 13.5l68.6 141.3 153.2 22.6c9 1.3 16.5 7.6 19.3 16.3s.5 18.1-5.9 24.5L433.6 328.4l26.2 155.6c1.5 9-2.2 18.1-9.7 23.5s-17.3 6-25.3 1.7l-137-73.2L151 509.1c-8.1 4.3-17.9 3.7-25.3-1.7s-11.2-14.5-9.7-23.5l26.2-155.6L31.1 218.2c-6.5-6.4-8.7-15.9-5.9-24.5s10.3-14.9 19.3-16.3l153.2-22.6L266.3 13.5C270.4 5.2 278.7 0 287.9 0z&quot;&#x2F;&gt;
        &lt;&#x2F;svg&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;count&quot;&gt;-&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
      &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
      &lt;span class=&quot;forks&quot;&gt;
        &lt;svg width=&quot;16&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; fill=&quot;currentColor&quot;&gt;
          &lt;path d=&quot;M5 5.372v.878c0 .414.336.75.75.75h4.5a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75v-.878a2.25 2.25 0 1 1 1.5 0v.878a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25h-1.5v2.128a2.251 2.251 0 1 1-1.5 0V8.5h-1.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3.5 6.25v-.878a2.25 2.25 0 1 1 1.5 0ZM5 3.25a.75.75 0 1 0-1.5 0 .75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0Zm6.75.75a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5Zm-3 8.75a.75.75 0 1 0-1.5 0 .75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0Z&quot;&#x2F;&gt;
        &lt;&#x2F;svg&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;count&quot;&gt;-&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
      &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
    &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
  &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;repo-description small secondary&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;repo-tags small accent&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Usage:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;markdown&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#151515;color:#e8e8d3;&quot; class=&quot;language-markdown &quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-markdown&quot; data-lang=&quot;markdown&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{gh_repo(owner=&amp;quot;rust-lang&amp;quot;, repo=&amp;quot;rust&amp;quot;)} # This would be double curly brackets
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
</content>
        
